description:
Lineage Journey is pleased to announce the release of a new interactive Reformation Study Guide series
This series of 5 books is designed as a companion material to the powerful historical documentary series Lineage Journey. The content includes; extended articles, videos, study questions perfect for groups, exclusive on location photographs taken by the Lineage Journey team, and much more!

Purchase the Reformation Study Guides on Apple Books today.
